OL,3,CMP says social media may cause
OL,4,Cincreased threats
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports political
OL,7,Fcorrespondent Andrew Misra reports
OL,9,FMP Tim Farron says social media could
OL,10,Fbe why politicians receive more
OL,11,Fthreats from the public, after the
OL,12,Fannouncement of a #31 million package
OL,13,Fwhich aims to strengthen security for
OL,14,FMPs.
OL,16,FThe new policy will be spent on
OL,17,Fcreating points of contact for elected
OL,18,Fmembers to raise their concerns,
OL,19,Fpolice protection, patrols and the
OL,20,Fcapacity for private security measures.
