OL,6,FThe Liberal Democrat MP for
OL,7,FWestmorland and Lonsdale said: "It
OL,8,Ffeels like it's got worse over the
OL,9,Flast couple of decades, it might just
OL,10,Fbe that 20 years ago social media
OL,11,Fwasn't such a thing.
OL,13,F"I remember being sat down in members
OL,14,Flobby a few years ago by a member of
OL,15,Fthe Metropolitan Police and being told
OL,16,Fthere had been a credible death threat
OL,17,Fagainst me, and how does it affect you?
OL,19,F"Well you first think about your
OL,20,Ffamily and what if something happened
OL,21,Fto me, what would it mean for them?"
