OL,6,F"We won't be able to enjoy the easy
OL,7,Faccess to our Members of Parliament
OL,8,Fthat we've enjoyed in the past. A
OL,9,Fconstituency surgery might look more
OL,10,Flike a constituency fortress in years
OL,11,Fto come.
